Daily schedules Preset times for your garage door to close or your myQ lights to turn on/off every day. Control two garage doors Add the ability to monitor, open and close a second garage door with an additional garage door sensor (SKU: 821LMC-SENSOR, sold separately). Amazon Key In-Garage Delivery Safe and Secure Packages Enables secure in-garage delivery for Amazon Prime packages. Real-Time Updates Monitor and control your deliveries from your smartphone.     As the owner of an older garage door opener, I was looking for a way to make it smarter and more convenient to use. That's when I discovered the Liftmaster myQ Smart Garage Control, and it has exceeded all my expectations. This wireless garage hub and sensor transforms my outdated garage door opener into a smart, connected device that I can control right from my smartphone. The setup process was incredibly easyI simply attached the sensor to my garage door and plugged in the hub, then followed the straightforward instructions in the myQ app to connect it to my home WiFi network. Once set up, I can open and close my garage door from anywhere using the myQ app on my smartphone, which is incredibly convenient when I'm away from home or just coming and going throughout the day. I also love the added security features, such as real-time alerts that notify me whenever the garage door is opened or closed, providing peace of mind knowing that my home is secure. Plus, the compatibility with both WiFi and Bluetooth ensures a reliable connection, even with older garage door openers like mine. Overall, I couldn't be happier with the Liftmaster myQ Smart Garage Controlit's a game-changer for anyone looking to upgrade their garage door opener to a smart, connected system.
